('367a97e2-d7ab-4981-9164-947cd872028d',    'AI Engineer',     'netflix', 'https://netflix.com/in/jobs',     '<h3>Company Description</h3><p>Netflix is the worlds leading streaming entertainment service with over 260 million paid memberships in over 190 countries enjoying TV series, documentaries, and feature films across a wide variety of genres and languages. At Netflix, we push the boundaries of storytelling and technology, enabling content creators and engineers to deliver seamless and scalable user experiences worldwide.</p><h3>Job Description</h3><p>As an AI Engineer at Netflix, you will play a key role in developing and deploying machine learning models and intelligent systems that power personalized experiences, content recommendations, and business decision-making across the platform. Based in Mumbai, India, you will collaborate with cross-functional teams spanning product, engineering, and data science to build and optimize AI solutions at scale.</p><p>This role is ideal for an engineer with a strong foundation in machine learning and deep learning who thrives in a fast-paced, data-rich environment and is passionate about solving real-world problems using AI technologies.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Design, build, and deploy end-to-end machine learning models for recommendation systems, content understanding, and personalization.</li><li>Collaborate with product managers, data scientists, and engineers to define AI-driven features and improve user engagement.</li><li>Work with large-scale datasets to perform feature engineering, model training, evaluation, and optimization.</li><li>Leverage tools and frameworks like TensorFlow, PyTorch, and MLFlow to scale training and deployment pipelines.</li><li>Implement scalable APIs and services to serve machine learning models in production environments.</li><li>Monitor and maintain model performance post-deployment, including data drift analysis and retraining strategies.</li><li>Participate